WEBVTT

00:09:58.851 --> 00:10:00.106
What were those?

00:10:00.515 --> 00:10:02.791
One -- most important of all --

00:10:02.815 --> 00:10:04.629
the freedom of speech.

00:10:04.653 --> 00:10:06.810
This was an innovative idea at the time.

00:10:06.834 --> 00:10:09.093
Namely, that if you were out of power,

00:10:09.117 --> 00:10:11.875
you could still say
that the government was terrible.

00:10:12.960 --> 00:10:14.120
Two,

00:10:14.890 --> 00:10:16.652
civil society organization.

00:10:17.051 --> 00:10:21.165
The capacity to put together
private groups, individuals,

00:10:21.189 --> 00:10:22.796
political parties and others

00:10:22.820 --> 00:10:25.953
who would organize to try to bring
about fundamental change.

00:10:27.933 --> 00:10:32.130
Perhaps most significantly
was the separation of powers --